Pre-requirements:
=================

For the matrix calculations you will need a decent C++ compiler and
blitz++ (Debian package or from http://oonumerics.org/blitz/)

Installation:
=============

Edit config.mk file to suit your local system.

Type:

  make
  make install

This will install things based on the PREFIX variable.  

To run the main program (genprob) you may need to add 

  PREFIX/lib

to your LD_LIBRARY_PATH

